data.description: Living Space Nestled in the rolling hills of the country-side, this freshly designed and built single-story home offers one-of-a kind living! On nearly 3 acres of sprawling landscape, this 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom abode features steel-frame construction, sound-deadening insulation, Hardi-plank exterior siding, and a metal roof to ensure decades of lasting durability. With its dedicated office space, an expansive covered and screened back porch (perfect for relaxing near the above-ground pool!), and a two-story metal Quonset Hut workshop, this property is a must-see! This home offers incredible conveniences like its own whole-home Generac generator, two propane tanks, separate full bathrooms for each bedroom, and Handicap accessibility. And for outdoor activities, you'll also enjoy the RV/boat carport, complete with waste water, power, and potable water connections, plus the screened-in part of the yard that hosts an array of fruit-bearing trees including Guava, Lemon, and Avocado. If you like cycling, hiking, kayaking or canoeing; you're in close proximity to the Withlacoochee River/Croom Recreational Park and the fair grounds. This almost off grid home is located just a few miles from I75, just off of ST 50. Head South to MacDill AFB/ James A. Hailey VA Hospital; East to Disney, North to Ocala/ Gainesville. For the ultimate in country living, this home ticks off all the check-marks!
